OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,FThe new prime minister has said No 10
OL,6,FNorth is "not a gimmick" as his plans
OL,7,Ffor devolution begin.
OL,9,FCivil servants have already started
OL,10,Fworking at Andy Burnham's new
OL,11,FManchester-based office, which, he
OL,12,Fsays, will cost taxpayers no extra
OL,13,Fmoney.
OL,15,FThose willing to move will be offered
OL,16,Frelocation packages, as reports that
OL,17,FWhitehall officials based in London
OL,18,Fare being encouraged to move to
OL,19,FManchester.
OL,21,FBut what is it, and what do we know?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
