OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,FWhat is No 10 North?
OL,7,FNo 10 in the North, based in
OL,8,FManchester, will focus on extending
OL,9,Fdevolution across the country.
OL,11,FBurnham has promised to improve
OL,12,Frelations between ministers and civil
OL,13,Fservants, and push powers to local
OL,14,Fleaders outside Westminster.
OL,16,FHe has called it "the nerve centre of
OL,17,Fa rewired Britain" and promised that
OL,18,F"the days of Whitehall fighting the
OL,19,Fdevolution power into the regions and
OL,20,Fnations are over for good."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
