OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,FWhat do we know about it so far?
OL,7,FStaff are already working in the new
OL,8,FNo 10 North including those both from
OL,9,FManchester and around the country.
OL,11,FBurnham "expects to work from No 10
OL,12,FNorth at least one day a week."
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister's official
OL,15,Fspokesman said: "It is based at
OL,16,Fexisting UK Government offices in
OL,17,FCentral Manchester and you can expect
OL,18,Fmore updates in due course.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
