OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,F"The running of No 10 North will be
OL,6,Fcovered by existing Cabinet Office
OL,7,Fbudgets. There is no additional cost
OL,8,Fto taxpayers."
OL,10,FIt has been widely reported that the
OL,11,Finitial location is Heron House.
OL,13,FWhat has Burnham said?
OL,15,FIn the first Cabinet meeting, Burnham
OL,16,Fsaid No 10 North is "not a gimmick"
OL,17,Fadding the "time for resisting
OL,18,Fdevolution was over".
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
