OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,FIn Downing Street, Burnham told his
OL,6,Ftop team on 21 July the two points on
OL,7,Fthe agenda for the meeting were the
OL,8,F"mission purpose of this Government
OL,9,Fand standards."
OL,11,FHe said: "The two are linked because
OL,12,Fwe will only deliver for people and
OL,13,Fmake hope feel real for people if we
OL,14,Fare pulling ourselves together in the
OL,15,Fsame direction and we have a really
OL,16,Fpositive working relationship, a sense
OL,17,Fof one team."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
