OL,3,CWhat is No 10 North?
OL,5,FHe also focused on unity, saying he
OL,6,Fwanted to hear from as many colleagues
OL,7,Fas time allowed, and AI, saying it was
OL,8,Frelevant to every department.
OL,10,FLords Leader Baroness Smith of
OL,11,FBasildon described the new northern
OL,12,Fbranch of Downing Street as "the
OL,13,Fengine room of devolution and good
OL,14,Fgrowth in every postcode, across
OL,15,FGovernment and the wider economy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
